  • Larger Narrow Edge 1080P Portable Screen：16:9 Portable IPS display, 1920 x 1080 full HD resolution and 144Hz high refresh rate, provide vivid images, clear movement and smooth game visual effects so that the picture is stable and not stuck. 17.3" With a larger screen, it will be more convenient and enjoyable to play games, watch videos, edit photos or work at home. It's an ideal choice for travelers, students, game players, programmers and everyone
  • Super Light Portable Second Screen: Portable monitor for laptop is only 0.2 inch at the thinnest point, 0.39 inch at the bottom and weighs only 2.12 lbs, which can easily accommodate each suitcase and backpack. It is also equipped with magnetic PU scratch-proof smart cover to provide comprehensive protection and can also be used as a bracket. You can work with a laptop screen extender anywhere, just like a large monitor in the office
  • Plug and Play&Widely Compatible: Only one USB-C cable is required for power supply and display signal transmission, and no driver is required. External monitor for laptop is equipped with mini HDMI ports and 2 full-featured Type-C, which enhance the stability of the port. It's compatible with most laptops, PCs, Macbooks, tablets, phones, PS5/PS4, Xbox, Switch and other devices.
  • 3 in 1 Multimode: 3-1 Mode portable external monitor (copy/expand/2nd screen) can meet your various needs. You can share content on the same screen and expand the screen for meetings to improve productivity. This will be very helpful when some problems with the screen connected to the device. You can also set the monitor horizontally or vertically as needed. It's the best assistant for Work at home, home entertainment, travel for work and outdoor telework to expand the screen
  • Necessary Cables Included： Laptop external monitor comes with all the required accessories: 2 * USB C to USB C cables, 1 * mini HDMI to HDMI cable, and 1 * wall charger. Some electronic devices without HDMI ports and full-function C ports may not be compatible. You can consult our online technical support

  • Joseph Luke
    5.0 out of 5 starsVerified Purchase
    Very Good Portable Monitor
    Reviewed in the United States on November 18, 2023
    Style: 15.6"1080p
    Got this as a second monitor for when I'm traveling. I'm surprised at how good it is for the money (~$76 when I bought it and at time of review). It includes all cables and a cover. It's literally plug and play - hook up the USB C from my laptop to... See more
    Got this as a second monitor for when I'm traveling. I'm surprised at how good it is for the money (~$76 when I bought it and at time of review).

    It includes all cables and a cover. It's literally plug and play - hook up the USB C from my laptop to the USB C on the monitor and voila! I have a second monitor. I'm using it with a Windows laptop so setting up the second monitor (location, which is primary, etc.) is simple: right-click on the desktop, select Display Settings.

    My laptop monitor is OLED so I knew that there was no way a non-OLED monitor would match it in either color or HDR. Out of the box, the colors are a bit off, but I was happy to find that this monitor it has fairly comprehensive adjustment settings. and I managed get it to be pretty good. If I wasn't comparing to an OLED screen, it would be perfect.

    I was recently at a cafe where someone else had a different portable monitor, one that is available here on Amazon for over $100. Neither of us could tell the difference in quality or image. Its a good monitor. Last note, I don't use the monitor for gaming so can't comment on that.

    The speakers work fine. They are fairly weak but I never intended to use them since my laptop speakers are very good.

    Overall, a very good monitor.

    The only thing I wish it had was a better case for transporting it. While it has a cover, a more robust case that would protect the screen from damage is almost required if you intend on putting this in your backpack, etc.

    I'd give this 4-4.5 stars, but for the price compared to other offerings on Amazon, it's a 5 star product.
